            <div type="translation" xml:lang="en" resp="#AA">
                <p>Sacred to Silvanus Augustus. In honour of Lucius Statius Onesimus, sexvir, and in the memory of Gaius Statius Primigenius, Augustalis, by decree of the decurions [and?] to Lucius Statius Hermes. Lucius Statius Encolpus, sexvir, [set this up].</p>
